featured_reviews.review_id:
Manmad junction.
The station has only one ticket counter.
Little bit rush at ticket counter.

There are 5-6 active railway platform at manmad station.
Railway canteen and water facility are available at every platform.

Apart from Railway Station.
Manmad has
Rickshaw
Taxi
Bus
And TUMm TUMm
As a basic transport facility from Manmad Railway Station to various destination.

From manmad Railway Station to Sai nagar Shirdi or Shirdi temple.
The local transport charges from 100/- per person. (Depends upon season and day charges may be varied).

Street foods are available outside the Stations .

All Express and local passengers trains stop here basically for 5-10 minutes.
